  "prompt": "Is there any good placement at northern India engineering college?",
  "response": "As of my last update, Northern India Engineering College (NIEC), located in Delhi, is known for its engineering programs, and it generally has a decent placement record. Many companies visit the campus for recruitment, and students typically secure placements in various fields such as IT, finance, manufacturing, and core engineering.\n\nThe effectiveness of placements can depend on several factors, including the specific engineering branch, overall student performance, and market conditions each year. Generally, branches like Computer Science and Engineering often see higher placement rates compared to other branches.\n\nFor the most current information on placements, including statistics, top recruiters, and trends, I recommend checking the official NIEC website or contacting the college's placement cell directly. They can provide the latest details and success stories from recent graduates.",
